author: lundblad
msg: Support ignoring whitespace and eol style changes in svn blame.
* subversion/include/svn_client.h
(svn_client_blame3): New version of the API with a diff_options argument
added.
(svn_client_blame2): Deprecate.
* subversion/libsvn_client/blame.c
(file_rev_baton): Add diff_options field.
(add_file_blame): Use svn_diff_diff_2() instead of deprecated API.
(svn_client_blame3): New version.  Initialize the diff_options field of the
file_rev_baton.
(svn_client_blame2): Wrap the new version.
* subversion/svn/blame-cmd.c
(svn_cl__blame): Use new blame API.  Get options from the extensions
cmdline option.
* subversion/svn/main.c (svn_cl__cmd_table): Add -x to the blame command.
